===Etymology===
{{zh-ref|Schuessler (2007)}} takes its first appearance in {{w|Chu Ci}} as suggestive of foreign origin. Possibly related to:
* {{cog|tai-pro|*C̥.doːjᴬ||mountain}} (whence {{cog|th|ดอย}}, {{cog|skb|tr=rɔ:jᴬ¹}}, {{cog|za|ndoi}})
* {{cog|hmx-pro|*glaɨᴰ||mountain}}, or
* {{w|Austroasiatic languages|Austroasiatic}}, e.g. {{cog|mkh-mmn|tr=duiw|t=hill, hilltop}}

Possibly connected with {{och-l|屯|id=1}}.

